1 A BILL for an Act to create and enact chapter 27-27.1 and a new subsection to section
2 30.1-28-07 of the North Dakota Century Code, relating to an office of guardianship and
3 conservatorship and the removal of a guardian; to amend and reenact section 30.1-29-15 and
